All Classes

Class Summary 
Class Description
AdminController
The AdminController controls all the behaviors of the screen and button in the Admin Dashboard.
Album
The Album class stores information related to the User's album
AlbumController
The Album Controller class controls the behaviors of the screens and buttons in the Album Display.
LoginController
LoginController controls all the behavior of the screen and buttons in the login screen.
Photo
The Photo class contains all the information pertaining to a photo.
PhotoController
PhotoController class controls all the behaviors of the screen and button in the photo view screen
Photos
Photos class is where the main method will go and initiate the application.
SearchController
The Search Controller controls all the behaviors of the screen and button in the search photos screen.
Serialization
The Serialization class handles storing the object data (the current album, the user arraylist and the current album)
Tag
The Tag class is where the tagName and tagValue will be stored for any photo.
TagType
TagType class defines the type for a tag.
User
The User class stores the information related to the User.
UserController
The UserController controls all the behaviors of the screen and button in the User Dashboard.
